'''Boesmanspruit''', or '''Boesman Spruit''', is a small stream originating south of [[Secunda, Mpumalanga|Secunda]], [[Mpumalanga]], [[South Africa]], it runs from there in a southwesterly direction until it joins the [[Waterval River]] (English: Water Fall River; the English name is never used however).

